item.title: Login is bugged. (help please)
item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

RegalX:

If it’s ok for you, you need to figure out what’s different between you and others. Is your java version newer? I had a problem with my webclient and the fix was for me to downgrade my java to JDK 6. If you use JDK 7, try and compile the files with JDK 6.

JDK6 users wouldn’t even be able to load a JDK7 jarred file because they are not compatible.

OT: It looks like you have been messing with your resetimageproducers method.

Read full topic
